These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: dancing, reading, gardening, magic-tricks
The people have 4 different jobs:  software-developer, accountant, firefighter, coach
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: salsa, folk, rock, blues
4 different pets are kept: goldfish, guinea-pig, chinchilla, pony
1. the accountant is the person who's hobby is dancing##1
2. the fan of blues is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
3. the fan of rock is the software-developer##1
4. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the accountant##1
5. the firefighter is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
6. the fan of salsa is on the left of the fan of folk##1
7. the accountant is the owner of the goldfish##1
8. the fan of folk is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1
9. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby         | dancing  | magic-tricks  | reading | gardening |
| Job           | accountant | software-developer | coach  | firefighter  |
| Music-Genre   | blues       | rock      | salsa | folk      |
| Pet           | goldfish          | guinea-pig     | chinchilla    | pony     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, 7up, mirinda, milk
There 4 different types of food: cauliflower, lime, onion, peas
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: rock, salsa, d&b, country
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: weightlifting, badminton, swimming, skateboarding
1. the person eating cauliflower is on the far right##1
2. the fan of country is the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
3. the person eating onion is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
4. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left of the person eating lime##1
5. the fan of country is on the left of the fan of rock##1
6. the person drinking mirinda is the fan of d&b##1
7. the fan of salsa is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
8. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
9. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3     |     4      |
| Beverage      | mirinda     | hot-chocolate       | 7up | milk        |
| Food          | peas     | lime       | onion   | cauliflower   |
| Music-Genre   | d&b      | salsa       | country     | rock    |
| Sport         | swimming | skateboarding | weightlifting | badminton |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: sprite, water, fanta, lemonade
The people have 4 different jobs:  fisherman, paramedic, software-developer, manager
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: mystery, superhero, sports, spy
4 different pets are kept: cat, fish, horse, snake
 1. the person drinking lemonade is the owner of the snake##1
 2. the person drinking fanta is on the far right##1
 3. the person watching sports movies is on the far right##1
 4. the owner of the horse is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
 5. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1
 6. the person watching mystery movies is on the left of the person watching superhero movies##1
 7. the person watching superhero movies is on the right of the paramedic##1
 8. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the fisherman##1
 9. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
10. the person drinking fanta is the manager##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |     3      |       4        |
| Beverage      | water | sprite       | lemonade        | fanta        |
| Job           | paramedic   | software-developer | fisherman   | manager |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery     | superhero    | spy | sports        |
| Pet           | horse         | cat  | snake       | fish         |

