3. the fan of country is on the far right##1
4. the entrepreneur is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
5. the fan of country is on the right of the fan of indie##1
6. the fan of soul is on the right of the nurse##1
7. the entrepreneur is on the right of the electrician##1
8. the japanese is on the far right##1
9. the owner of the frog is the colombian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3     |      4      |
