.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-5::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  engineer, writer, entrepreneur, photographer
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, musical, documentary, fantasy
There are 4 different nationalities: nigerian, spanish, dutch, argentine
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: swimming, tennis, soccer, climbing
