2. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the engineer##1
3. the person who's sport is tennis is on the far left##1
4. the spanish is on the left of the nigerian##1
5. the argentine is on the right of the person who's sport is climbing##1
6. the person who's sport is climbing is the dutch##1
7. the nigerian is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1
8. the writer is on the right of the person watching musical movies##1
9. the person watching animation movies is on the right of the entrepreneur##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |       3       |      4       |
| Job           | engineer  | entrepreneur    | writer | photographer |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary      | musical    | animation         | fantasy    |
| Nationality   | spanish   | nigerian     | dutch          | argentine      |
| Sport         | tennis | swimming | climbing      | soccer      |

