.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-6::.
There 4 different types of food: lime, garlic, pumpkin, kiwi
The people have 4 different jobs:  scientist, musician, entrepreneur, pilot
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: documentary, zombie, disaster, epic
4 different pets are kept: rabbit, ferret, goldfish, turtle
 1. the person eating pumpkin is the person watching documentary movies##1
 2. the person eating lime is the person watching zombie movies##1
 3. the scientist is the person watching documentary movies##1
 4. the owner of the goldfish is the person eating lime##1
 5. the person watching disaster movies is the pilot##1
 6. the person eating pumpkin is on the left of the person eating garlic##1
 7. the entrepreneur is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
 8. the person watching documentary movies is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
 9. the entrepreneur is on the far left##1
10. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the person eating garlic##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |     3      |     4     |
| Food          | lime  | kiwi | pumpkin     | garlic |
| Job           | entrepreneur  | pilot      | scientist | musician    |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie | disaster  | documentary    | epic  |
| Pet           | goldfish   | turtle       | rabbit       | ferret      |

