.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-7::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, juice, lemonade, sprite
The people have 4 different hobbies: hiking, rock-climbing, chess, collecting
4 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, dog, chinchilla, cat
The people use 4 different means of transport: roller, bike, jet-ski, bus
 1. the owner of the guinea-pig is the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
 2. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
 3. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person who's hobby is chess##1
 4. the owner of the dog is on the left of the person who's hobby is chess##1
 5. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
 6. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
 7. the owner of the guinea-pig is the person driving the jet-ski##1
 8. the person drinking milk is on the far left##1
 9. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
10. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Beverage    | milk | juice     | lemonade    | sprite |
| Hobby       | hiking | chess    | collecting | rock-climbing |
| Pet         | dog   | chinchilla  | cat        | guinea-pig    |
| Transport   | bus   | bike | roller    | jet-ski |

